@startuml
actor Student
participant Browser
participant "EduSecure API" as API
database DB

Student -> Browser : enter email + password
Browser -> API : POST /login over HTTP
API -> DB : query plaintext password
DB --> API : plaintext password record
API --> Browser : token over HTTP

note right of Browser
Credentials and token can be intercepted.
end note

note right of DB
If the database is exposed,
passwords are readable immediately.
end note
@enduml

